<section id="To_approve_a_provisioning_request1" remap="TID_15547">
	<title>Approving a Provisioning Request</title>
	<para>
		After a user creates provisioning request, administrators have the ability to approve the request and allow <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> to complete virtual machine or instance creation.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Approve a Provisioning Request</title> 
		<!--step>
			<para>
				Log in as a user with administrator or super administrator rights to the <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> console.
			</para>
		</step-->
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Services</guimenu><guisubmenu>Requests</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click on the request you want to approve.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Type in a <guilabel>Reason</guilabel> for the approval.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1852.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>(Approve this request)</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>